{"tid":950410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"弟弟失明癱瘓住院　哥哥竟趴身上摩擦猥褻","createTime":"2018-12-21T13:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T03:01:54.000Z","uid":80051,"like":1050,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"54ca8e38bd7ec7c98bf26232431d2451165d76c7","tid":950410,"uid":80051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"這什麼劇情？桃園一名彭姓男子在今年8月2日，涉嫌趁弟弟中風住院無力反抗時，將弟弟翻身後以下體摩擦其肛門至射精，因護理人員察覺有異便報警處理，桃園地檢署今依乘機猥褻罪將他聲請簡判。<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果日報》報導，警方調查，弟弟約50餘歲，因右側身軀癱瘓、雙眼失明中風住院，約60餘歲的哥哥彭男，竟涉嫌把病床上的弟弟翻身成趴姿，再跪坐在弟弟身上，用下體摩擦其肛門直至射精。因護理人員發現哥哥異常的舉動，且幫病患換藥及擦身體時見到弟弟身上有不明液體，便報警處理，桃園地檢署今依乘機猥褻罪嫌將彭男聲請簡易判決處刑。（編輯：數位發展部）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/456662/?utm_campaign=twnext_social_nexttw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Fnews%2F456662%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwnext_social_nexttw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&d=Hr6YcpbB53ZKSqCYDQqOFBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f2dd7c70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nextmag.com.tw/realtimenews/news/456662/?utm_campaign=twnext_social_nexttw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f870fc7a0dbc36f2c88940e1275d2c7b88759f","tid":950410,"uid":140429,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59862fb901b66e4b35e6ea2391842e5bee072b22","tid":950410,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73852aa9082244867af5829428605956ce6c4b62","tid":950410,"uid":80051,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <